  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nForge\r\n\r\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\r\n\r\n- [X] Foundry\r\n- [ ] Foundryup\r\n\r\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\r\n\r\nforge script script/BroadcastTest.sol:BroadcastTest --rpc-url=$env:GOERLI_RPC_URL -vv\r\n\r\n### Operating System\r\n\r\nWindows\r\n\r\n### Describe the bug\r\n\r\nI have scripts that are failing simulation (reverting on onlyOwner checks of deployed contracts) because neither the startBroadcast() nor the startPrank() cheatcodes are updating msg.sender. \r\n\r\n```\r\n// SPDX-License-Identifier: Unlicensed\r\npragma solidity ^0.8.17;\r\n\r\nimport \"forge-std/Script.sol\";\r\n\r\ncontract BroadcastTest is Script {\r\n    function run() external {\r\n        uint256 deployerPrivateKey = vm.envUint(\"PRIVATE_KEY\");\r\n        address deployer = vm.addr(deployerPrivateKey);\r\n\r\n        // Initial \r\n        console.log(\"msg.sender should be deployer %s\", deployer);\r\n        console.log(\"msg.sender %s\", msg.sender);\r\n        \r\n        // Broadcast\r\n        console.log();\r\n        console.log(\"nvm.startBroadcast(deployerPrivateKey)...\");\r\n        vm.startBroadcast(deployerPrivateKey);\r\n        console.log(\"msg.sender %s\", msg.sender);\r\n        vm.stopBroadcast();\r\n        console.log(\"vm.stopBroadcast()\");\r\n\r\n        // Prank\r\n        console.log();\r\n        console.log(\"vm.startPrank(deployer)...\");\r\n        vm.startPrank(deployer);\r\n        console.log(\"msg.sender %s\", msg.sender);\r\n        vm.stopPrank();\r\n        console.log(\"vm.stopPrank()\");\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ forge script script/BroadcastTest.sol:BroadcastTest --rpc-url=$env:GOERLI_RPC_URL -vv     \r\n[⠒] Compiling...\r\n[⠑] Compiling 1 files with 0.8.17\r\n[⠃] Solc 0.8.17 finished in 602.18ms\r\nCompiler run successful\r\nScript ran successfully.\r\n\r\n== Logs ==\r\n  msg.sender should be deployer 0xd6E1fE2d44555597828eD5a7401A481a7654A530\r\n  msg.sender 0x1804c8AB1F12E6bbf3894d4083f33e07309d1f38\r\n\r\n  nvm.startBroadcast(deployerPrivateKey)...\r\n  msg.sender 0x1804c8AB1F12E6bbf3894d4083f33e07309d1f38\r\n  vm.stopBroadcast()\r\n\r\n  vm.startPrank(deployer)...\r\n  msg.sender 0x1804c8AB1F12E6bbf3894d4083f33e07309d1f38\r\n  vm.stopPrank()\r\n```\r\n\r\nHow have people been working around this?",
