    "body": "Seems like `msg.sender` is not set correctly when using `vm.startBroadcast(key)` at the top-level. It does work correctly when passing in the private key via `--private-key 0xabc..`. The `msg.sender` is however correctly set in external calls / deployments:\r\n\r\n```solidity\r\ncontract ABC {\r\n    constructor() {\r\n        console.log(\"ABC msg.sender\", msg.sender);\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n```\r\n  msg.sender should be deployer 0xf39Fd6e51aad88F6F4ce6aB8827279cffFb92266\r\n  msg.sender 0x1804c8AB1F12E6bbf3894d4083f33e07309d1f38\r\n  \r\n  vm.startBroadcast(deployerPrivateKey)\r\n  msg.sender 0x1804c8AB1F12E6bbf3894d4083f33e07309d1f38\r\n  ABC msg.sender 0xf39Fd6e51aad88F6F4ce6aB8827279cffFb92266\r\n  vm.stopBroadcast()\r\n```",
